pull.title: [Qt] further translation string updates
pull.body: @laanwj Perhaps we can get these also in for 0.10 :).

events.body: Seems low priority, I'd prefer to let this wait for the next release
We still have some other string changes left and likely enough time... just saying.
This now also changes the displayed license from MIT/X11 to just MIT in the executables!

@Diapolo Nice
I'm going to cherry-pick just that commit for now.
@laanwj Do as you like, I guess I don't have to understand ^^. But remember I collect small satoshis just via the Tip4Commit service ;).

Ideally you should do these kind of "cosmetic" changes to messages just after a release split off, not just before one. Invalidating translation messages now is a bad idea unless absolutely necessary.
